voices.mp3Text: There is no team in Axe!
There is no team in Axe!
Axe is calling it: It’s in the bag!
This was in the bag the day Axe was born!
There can be no battle till Axe is at hand. And Axe is.

text: On cast, hit 1 or more units

voices.mp3Text: You get nothing. Good day, sir!

text: Killing enemy, within 2 seconds after blink

voices.mp3Text: Mwa ha ha ha ha ha!
Ha ha ha ha ha ha!
Axe chops you down to size!
Axe warms his blade in your guts!
Twenty hacks from the axe of Axe!
Sheathe my axe in your bowels!
You might have been a fancyman in Heaven, but down here you are nothing next to Axe.
voices.name: Zeus

voices.mp3Text: Axe has no time for all this jibber jabber.
voices.name: Warlock

voices.mp3Text: Warlock, you should have picked a sharper weapon.
voices.name: Warlock

voices.mp3Text: Warlock, who is the smart one now?
voices.name: Warlock

voices.mp3Text: Axe hates to kill Oglodi, but it must be done.
voices.name: Warlock

voices.mp3Text: We are blood, true. But most of yours came out.
voices.name: Disruptor

voices.mp3Text: You were handsome like Axe. Axe doesn't like that.
voices.name: Disruptor

voices.mp3Text: Too much talking, not enough fighting.
voices.name: Invoker

voices.mp3Text: Big words cannot keep you safe from Axe.
voices.name: Invoker

voices.mp3Text: The Treant brought much wood for Axe to chop.
voices.name: Treant Protector

voices.mp3Text: More things for Axe to chop!
voices.name: Treant Protector

voices.mp3Text: Who said Axe fears spiders? Axe wants to know their name.
voices.name: Broodmother

voices.mp3Text: Doom Bringer brings doom. Axe brings axe!
voices.name: Doom

voices.mp3Text: Taste the Axe. Not this Axe, that axe!
voices.name: Pudge

voices.mp3Text: Your name is not Axe-world Destroyer!
voices.name: Outworld Devourer

voices.mp3Text: What is a tiny razor to a mighty Axe?
voices.name: Razor

voices.mp3Text: Each of Ursa's claws is like a little axe. Axe reluctantly approves.
voices.name: Ursa

voices.mp3Text: Axe has no time for such nonsense!
voices.name: Spectre

voices.mp3Text: Smallkeens should be scoured from the land!
voices.name: Alchemist

voices.mp3Text: For the Keenfolk, you weren't half bad.
voices.name: Sniper

voices.mp3Text: Axe cut you into more than four.
Axe cut you into more than four. Nine?
Axe cut you into more than four. Twenty?
Axe cut you into more than four. Hundreds?
Ha ha, the blade of Axe has tasted first blood!
Axe will whittle them down one by one.
You look like Axe, only slightly less.
voices.name: Disruptor

voices.mp3Text: That is a fearsome creature you ride, Disruptor.
voices.name: Disruptor

voices.mp3Text: Side by side, the Oglodi fight.
voices.name: Warlock

voices.mp3Text: The Oglodi shall take this fight.
voices.name: Warlock

voices.mp3Text: Warlock brings a book. Axe brings an axe.
voices.name: Warlock

voices.mp3Text: Axe is curious. Where did your face go?
voices.name: Faceless Void

voices.mp3Text: Undying, don't order Axe around and we'll get along just fine.
voices.name: Undying

voices.mp3Text: Don't worry, Treant, Axe does not come to chop you.
voices.name: Treant Protector

voices.mp3Text: Witch doctor, our enemies are in need of Axe-amination!
voices.name: Witch Doctor

voices.mp3Text: Tinker, eh? War is an Axe-act science!
voices.name: Tinker

voices.mp3Text: By his blade, Axe earns this purchase.
Don't worry, precious axe. Blink Dagger does not come to chop.
voices.name: Blink Dagger (2250)

voices.mp3Text: The Axe's edge will never dull!
voices.name: Aegis of the Immortal

voices.mp3Text: The Axe's edge is keen again!
Axe is all the reinforcement this army needs!
From the Red Mist, Axe returns!
Axe returns. The war may now continue!
Ha ha ha ha ha ha!
Axe is back and ready to whack! And also hack!
Axe does not need this, but no one else shall have it.

text: Third and more attempts within 10 seconds
Third and more attempts within 10 seconds

voices.mp3Text: So many skulls to cleave. So many bodies to throw on the pile.
No business but war. No family but death. No mercy but the grave!
Bottom is missing according to Axe.
Ha ha ha ha ha ha!
Axe likes this so much words fail Axe.
